reviewText: G​reat course, but final assignment requires peer review, and it looks like some assignments haven't been graded in two years. Can't recieve certificate until a peer reviews your final assignment.

There are never enough peer review opportunities available when I have completed my assignment and am ready to review others' assignments. As a result, I have to wait multiple days, sometimes even a full week in order to completed a course within this program.

Update...several days later, and still no peer review available. This program is dysfunctional and I would never recommend it to anyone. I would like a refund asap!

This course is 90% "go read this on your own" instruction, 9% sitting around waiting for your peer review assignments to be graded, and 1% judging horrible typos and gramatical errors questioning if this really leads to any credible certification in the end. It's easy! If you work in this industry at all you can pass this course in your sleep. That is as long as you have any peers around to grade your assignments.
